= 0.3.1 -> 0.3.2 =

 * Fix shebang
 * Python3 support

= 0.3.0 -> 0.3.1 =

 * Fix a build issue with the latest gobject-introspection
 * Fix typos

= 0.2.0 -> 0.3.0 =

 * Add feature tags support
 * Fix the close button behavior from window manager.

= 0.1.5 -> 0.2.0 =

 * Improve UI
 * Add embedded bitmap support (libeasyfc 0.11 is required)
 * Hide the language ordering feature when it's not supported
 * Add font substitution support (libeasyfc 0.11 is required)
 * Embed resource files into the binary.

= 0.1.4 -> 0.1.5 =

 * Translation Updates
 * Enhancement
   * Use the pangram from Pango API instead of the own one.

= 0.1.3 -> 0.1.4 =

 * Bug Fix
   * Fix the version check code.

= 0.1.2 -> 0.1.3 =

 * Enhancement
   * Allow users to set hintstyle for both hinting mode
 * Bug Fix
   * Do not validate the font if the classification filter is turned off

